WEBVTT

00:01.697 --> 00:03.525
[Mindy]
THE EMPIRE STATE BUILDING
ON VALENTINE'S DAY,

00:03.568 --> 00:05.396
THE MOST ROMANTIC BUILDING
IN THE WORLD

00:05.440 --> 00:06.963
ON THE MOST ROMANTIC DAY
OF THE YEAR.

00:07.007 --> 00:09.879
SO MANY MEMORABLE ROMANCES
HAVE PLAYED OUT HERE.

00:09.922 --> 00:11.837
DEBORAH KERR
AND CARY GRANT

00:11.881 --> 00:13.535
IN AN AFFAIR TO REMEMBER.

00:13.578 --> 00:15.363
[as James Cagney]
"GIVE ME A SMOOCH,
RIGHT ON THE MUG, SEE?"

00:15.406 --> 00:17.800
I DO A PRETTY SPOT-ON
CARY GRANT.

00:17.843 --> 00:20.933
AND OF COURSE,
THE SECOND-BEST ROMANTIC COMEDY

00:20.977 --> 00:23.023
THAT MEG RYAN
AND TOM HANKS EVER MADE:

00:23.066 --> 00:24.589
SLEEPLESS IN SEATTLE.

00:24.633 --> 00:26.983
EVERY COUPLE WEEKS,
I BUY A TICKET

00:27.027 --> 00:28.811
AND HANG OUT IN THE LOBBY
OF THE EMPIRE STATE BUILDING

00:28.854 --> 00:30.726
TO SEE IF I WILL MEET
MY ONE TRUE LOVE.

00:30.769 --> 00:33.642
CAPTAIN, SHE'S BACK.

00:35.122 --> 00:36.166
SO YOU COME HERE REGULARLY

00:36.210 --> 00:38.081
TO MONITOR THE BASE
OF THE BUILDING.

00:38.125 --> 00:39.604
I'M HERE TO MEET
THAT SPECIAL SOMEONE,

00:39.648 --> 00:41.954
AND WHEN I DO,
WE'RE GONNA GO TO THE TOP,

00:41.998 --> 00:43.956
AND THEN, BOOM!
FIREWORKS.

00:44.000 --> 00:45.088
AND WHO IS THAT PERSON?

00:45.132 --> 00:46.394
I HAVEN'T MET HIM YET,

00:46.437 --> 00:47.830
BUT I CAN TELL
WHEN I FIND HIM,

00:47.873 --> 00:51.007
WE'RE GOING TO SPEND
ETERNITY TOGETHER.

00:51.051 --> 00:52.052
COULD YOU DESCRIBE HIM?

00:52.095 --> 00:54.010
ALL RIGHT, WELL,
HE'S IN HIS MID-30s.

00:54.054 --> 00:57.622
HE IS TALL, DARK,
INTENSE, MYSTERIOUS--

00:57.666 --> 00:59.059
YOU UNDERSTAND WHY
WHAT YOU'RE TELLING US

00:59.102 --> 01:01.017
WOULD CAUSE US
SERIOUS CONCERN.

01:01.061 --> 01:02.279
YEAH. I CAN'T HELP IT,

01:02.323 --> 01:04.107
YOU KNOW,
EVEN THOUGH IT'S DANGEROUS,

01:04.151 --> 01:05.500
BECAUSE I AM
A TRUE BELIEVER.

01:05.543 --> 01:08.285
HEY, WE'RE GONNA NEED MILLER
FROM HOMELAND SECURITY.

01:08.329 --> 01:09.852
