01:09.895 --> 01:11.158
THAT'S A COOL SHOW.

01:11.201 --> 01:12.724
WHY DO YOU HAVE A BAG
WITH A PASSPORT

01:12.768 --> 01:13.986
AND THREE CELL PHONES?

01:14.030 --> 01:16.032
OKAY, WELL,
THIS IS FOR THE INTERNET,

01:16.076 --> 01:17.686
THIS IS FOR TEXTING,

01:17.729 --> 01:20.254
AND THIS FLIP PHONE
IS BECAUSE I DO NOT KNOW

01:20.297 --> 01:21.690
HOW TO TRANSFER
MY OLD CONTACTS.

01:21.733 --> 01:24.258
YOU KNOW, WE'VE BEEN
SPENDING SO MUCH TIME

01:24.301 --> 01:25.694
TALKING ABOUT ME

01:25.737 --> 01:28.088
