ASKED YOU ANYTHING.

01:28.131 --> 01:29.132
WHAT ARE YOU INTO?

01:29.176 --> 01:30.568
PROTECTING THIS BUILDING.

01:30.612 --> 01:33.223
OOH, I LOVE THAT.
IT'S SO OLD-FASHIONED.

01:33.267 --> 01:34.833
YOU HAVE GREAT FACIAL HAIR.

01:34.877 --> 01:36.052
I LOVE A GUY
WITH A BEARD.

01:36.096 --> 01:37.184
CAN I TOUCH IT?

01:37.227 --> 01:38.576
HANDS ON THE TABLE, PLEASE.

01:38.620 --> 01:40.274
HEY, IT'S COOL
IF YOU'RE INTO ME.

01:40.317 --> 01:42.189
