01:43.712 --> 01:45.366
I'M JUST SAYING
I DON'T SEE A WEDDING RING.

01:45.409 --> 01:49.761
IS THERE A MRS. CONFEDERATED
SECURITY SOLUTIONS?

01:50.980 --> 01:52.155
OH, MY GOD.

01:52.199 --> 01:54.201
