IT'S YOU.

02:46.122 --> 02:47.384
OKAY, THAT IS NOT ME.

02:47.428 --> 02:48.516
WHEN I LAY ON THE FLOOR,
IT'S ADORABLE,

02:48.559 --> 02:49.473
AND IT IS TRAGIC.

02:49.517 --> 02:50.735
WHEN YOU LAY ON THE FLOOR,

02:50.779 --> 02:52.563
