AN UPSIDE-DOWN LADYBUG.

02:52.607 --> 02:54.391
MY GOD, AM I THE ONLY PERSON
NOT CRAWLING ABOUT

02:54.435 --> 02:55.697
ON THE FLOOR TODAY?

02:55.740 --> 02:57.351
YOU GUYS, I DROPPED
A MIKE AND IKE ON THE FLOOR.

02:57.394 --> 02:58.917
I NEED ALL EYES ON THIS.

02:58.961 --> 03:00.354
DANNY, YOU'RE A GROWN-UP.
GET UP.

03:00.397 --> 03:01.529
YOU'RE RIGHT.

03:01.572 --> 03:02.660
I'M GONNA GET
MYSELF TOGETHER.

03:02.704 --> 03:04.096
I'M GONNA PULL IT TOGETHER.

03:04.140 --> 03:06.447
I'M GONNA MEET ANOTHER GIRL.
IT'S GONNA BE GOOD.

03:06.490 --> 03:07.796
