WHEN I AM HEARTBROKEN,

03:07.839 --> 03:09.580
IT IS ACTUALLY BEST
TO THROW MYSELF INTO WORK.

03:09.624 --> 03:11.539
WHICH IS WHY, ON THURSDAY, I AM GOING TO DO YOU

03:11.582 --> 03:13.323
THE FAVOR OF GIVING YOU
ALL OF MY PATIENTS

03:13.367 --> 03:14.498
FOR THE WHOLE NIGHT.

03:14.542 --> 03:15.673
MINDY, IT'S FINE.

03:15.717 --> 03:16.631
I'LL LOOK AFTER YOUR PATIENTS
ON THURSDAY.

03:16.674 --> 03:17.806
YOU ENJOY
YOUR VALENTINE'S DAY.

03:17.849 --> 03:19.373
OH, IS THURSDAY
VALENTINE'S DAY?
YES. NICE.

03:19.416 --> 03:21.505
I-I HADN'T REMEMBERED.
OKAY.

03:21.549 --> 03:22.593
WAIT, HOW COME YOU,
OF ALL PEOPLE,

03:22.637 --> 03:23.899
