SOMETHING OF A MINEFIELD.

03:28.556 --> 03:30.688
"OH, A DOZEN ROSES.
YOU MUST REALLY LIKE ME."

03:30.732 --> 03:32.560
"HEY, DO YOU WANT TO SHARE
A DESSERT?"

03:32.603 --> 03:33.474
"OH, THAT MEANS YOU MUST WANT
TO MEET MY PARENTS,

03:33.517 --> 03:34.475
WHO LIVE IN MINNEAPOLIS."

03:34.518 --> 03:36.259
IT'S AN EMOTIONAL BOSNIA.

03:36.303 --> 03:37.695
THINK I'LL SIT IT OUT, THANKS. WELL, GREAT.

03:37.739 --> 03:40.002
THEN I CAN HAVE VALENTINE'S DAY
WITH JAMIE.

03:40.045 --> 03:42.091
AS IN JAMIE AND LUCY?

03:42.134 --> 03:43.135
NOW, THERE'S A GREAT COUPLE.

03:43.179 --> 03:44.615
NOPE,
NOT AS IN JAMIE AND LUCY.

03:44.659 --> 03:46.051
AS IN JAMIE AND MINDY.

03:46.095 --> 03:47.749
BUT AREN'T YOU WORRIED
ABOUT THE INCREDIBLE CHEMISTRY

03:47.792 --> 03:48.837
THEY SEEM TO HAVE?

03:48.880 --> 03:50.186
THEY DON'T HAVE
GOOD CHEMISTRY.

03:50.230 --> 03:51.492
