WITH JAMIE.

03:51.535 --> 03:55.017
I'M REALLY LONELY.

03:55.060 --> 03:57.324
[Jamie]
MoMA WAS SUCH
A FUN IDEA, MINDY.

03:57.367 --> 04:00.152
