THEY'RE LESS INTIMIDATING

04:01.632 --> 04:03.634
'CAUSE I THINK
I COULD DO THE ART.

04:03.678 --> 04:05.070
OH, YOU KNOW WHAT?
YOUR STICKER IS COMING OFF.

04:05.114 --> 04:06.246
OH, ACTUALLY, LEAVE IT.

04:06.289 --> 04:07.334
I LIKE PEOPLE
TO KNOW THAT I HAD

04:07.377 --> 04:08.726
A MORE CULTURAL DAY
THAN THEY DID.

04:08.770 --> 04:10.293
OH, IT'S LIKE THE ARTSY VERSION
OF "I VOTED."

04:10.337 --> 04:12.382
OH, YES, I HAVE
A SKI LIFT TICKET

04:12.426 --> 04:13.731
ON MY PARKA
FROM TWO YEARS AGO.

04:13.775 --> 04:14.950
WHEN YOU TEACH LATIN
FOR A LIVING,

04:14.993 --> 04:16.386
IT HELPS TO LOOK LIKE
A HUGE JOCK SOMETIMES.

04:16.430 --> 04:17.518
HEY, YOU GUYS.

04:17.561 --> 04:18.519
SORRY I'M LATE.

04:18.562 --> 04:19.781
NO, NOT AT ALL.

04:19.824 --> 04:21.478
IT TURNS OUT
THE DEFENDANT'S GANG

04:21.522 --> 04:23.306
HAD A COPY OF MY HOME ADDRESS,
BECAME A THING.WHAT?

04:23.350 --> 04:24.568
WHAT?OH, MY GOD.

04:24.612 --> 04:26.266
