IN THE EYE AND PUTS THEM

04:30.661 --> 04:32.010
IN PRISON FOR THE REST
OF THEIR LIVES.

04:32.054 --> 04:33.403
WOW. SO IMPORTANT.

04:33.447 --> 04:35.405
I MEAN, SPEAKING
OF STRESSFUL SITUATIONS,

04:35.449 --> 04:36.624
I DELIVERED A BABY
LAST NIGHT.

04:36.667 --> 04:37.886
HE DID NOT WANT
TO BE BORN.

04:37.929 --> 04:39.061
HE WAS REALLY MAD
AT ME.

04:39.104 --> 04:40.584
I'M GLAD HE DIDN'T HAVE
MY HOME ADDRESS.

04:40.628 --> 04:41.803
[chuckles]THAT'S REALLY FUNNY.

04:41.846 --> 04:43.326
HEY, SERIOUSLY, THOUGH,
YOU KNOW,

04:43.370 --> 04:44.980
IF YOU EVER FEAR FOR YOUR SAFETY, YOU STILL HAVE A KEY.

04:45.023 --> 04:46.503
IF YOU EVER WANT TO STAY
AT MY PLACE,

04:46.547 --> 04:47.765
YOU KNOW YOU CAN, RIGHT?

04:47.809 --> 04:49.724
WELL, I WOULD RATHER TAKE ON
THE SINALOA CARTEL

04:49.767 --> 04:51.813
THAN DEAL WITH THE WATER
PRESSURE IN THIS GUY'S SHOWER.

04:51.856 --> 04:53.423
[laughs]
IT'S NOT THAT BAD.

04:53.467 --> 04:54.729
[laughs heartily]IT'S NOT THAT BAD.

04:54.772 --> 04:55.947
YOU'RE SO GREAT.

04:55.991 --> 04:57.993
YOU SHOULD HAVE
A BOYFRIEND.

04:58.036 --> 04:59.864
I WOULD LOVE TO MEET A COOL GUY,
EXCEPT ALL THE GUYS I MEET

04:59.908 --> 05:02.954
ARE EITHER 19-YEAR-OLD MURDERERS
OR 80-YEAR-OLD JUDGES.

05:02.998 --> 05:04.391
YOU KNOW WHAT, I THINK
I'M GONNA FIND YOU SOMEONE.

05:04.434 --> 05:06.001
NO, I REALLY WOULDN'T TRY.YEAH, GREAT.

05:06.044 --> 05:08.569
THIS GIRL IS THE PICKIEST DATER
I HAVE EVER MET IN MY LIFE.

05:08.612 --> 05:10.222
NO, NO, I'M ACTUALLY
A VERY GOOD MATCHMAKER.

05:10.266 --> 05:11.789
WELL, I WISH YOU LUCK,

05:11.833 --> 05:14.009
