GOOD ENOUGH FOR THIS GIRL.

05:14.052 --> 05:15.010
SO I WOULDN'T EVEN TRY.

05:15.053 --> 05:17.795
[Jamie] SO MINDY AT THE MUSEUM...

05:19.057 --> 05:20.972
AH, DANNY.

05:21.016 --> 05:22.887
TEAR UP THAT SUICIDE NOTE.
I HAVE GREAT NEWS.

05:22.931 --> 05:24.672
OKAY, THAT WASN'T
A SUICIDE NOTE.

05:24.715 --> 05:26.282
