05:27.675 --> 05:29.198
DANNY, I AM GOING
TO SET YOU UP ON A DATE.

05:29.241 --> 05:31.635
THIS MORNING YOU SAID I SHOULD
THROW MYSELF BACK INTO WORK.

05:31.679 --> 05:32.941
THAT WAS, LIKE,
SIX HOURS AGO, OKAY?

05:32.984 --> 05:33.942
