FOR SOME BUGS.

05:33.985 --> 05:35.117
YOU'RE GONNA LOVE
THIS GIRL.

05:35.160 --> 05:37.032
SHE IS PRETTY.
SHE IS SMART.

05:37.075 --> 05:39.121
