05:45.606 --> 05:46.607
OKAY, I DON'T KNOW.

05:46.650 --> 05:47.999
I JUST--I DON'T KNOW
IF I'M READY.

05:48.043 --> 05:49.871
WELL, YOU WOULD ALSO
BE DOING ME A HUGE FAVOR.

05:49.914 --> 05:51.351
IF YOU SPEND TIME
WITH LUCY,

05:51.394 --> 05:53.178
THEN JAMIE WON'T SPEND
AS MUCH TIME WITH HER.

05:53.222 --> 05:54.266
ALSO, THIS IS A BIG DEAL.

05:54.310 --> 05:55.355
I AM SETTING YOU UP
WITH SOMEONE.

05:55.398 --> 05:56.573
YOU NEVER SET ME UP
WITH ANYBODY.

05:56.617 --> 05:58.140
THAT'S NOT TRUE.
I HOOKED YOU UP WITH REYNALDO.

05:58.183 --> 06:00.011
YOUR GARBAGE MAN?
YEAH.

06:00.055 --> 06:01.970
HE WAS SMOKIN' HOT,
BUT HE WAS A LITTLE PRETENTIOUS.

06:02.013 --> 06:04.189
