IF I MAY SAY THAT.

06:04.233 --> 06:05.234
DANNY, PLEASE DO THIS
FOR ME.

06:05.277 --> 06:06.366
CAN I THINK ABOUT IT?
DANNY!

06:06.409 --> 06:07.497
YOU ARE SO SELFISH!

06:07.541 --> 06:08.846
