IF YOU'RE DEPRESSED!

06:08.890 --> 06:09.891
JUST HELP ME OUT FOR ONCE!OKAY, STOP--

06:09.934 --> 06:11.109
ALL RIGHT.I AM GONNA DIE ALONE

06:11.153 --> 06:12.284
