06:12.328 --> 06:14.722
I'LL GO ON ONE DATE
WITH HER, OKAY?

06:14.765 --> 06:16.114
ARE YOU SERIOUS?
ONE.

06:16.158 --> 06:17.420
OH, MY GOD, DANNY,
THANK YOU. THANK YOU.

06:17.464 --> 06:18.856
OKAY.WHEN EVERYONE'S
MEAN ABOUT YOU,

06:18.900 --> 06:20.292
I DEFEND YOU
MOST OF THE TIME.

06:20.336 --> 06:21.729
OKAY, I'M GOOD
ON THE HUG, THOUGH.

06:21.772 --> 06:23.208
THANKS.TO SHOW MY GRATITUDE

06:23.252 --> 06:24.862
FOR THIS KINDNESS,

06:24.906 --> 06:27.909
WE CAN CHOOSE ANY CITY
OF REAL HOUSEWIVESTO WATCH.

06:27.952 --> 06:29.998
[sighs]
MIAMI.

06:30.041 --> 06:31.042
YES.

06:31.086 --> 06:33.393
[women shouting on TV]

06:35.786 --> 06:37.571
DEBORAH, DO YOU LIKE
WORKING IN THE MORGUE?

06:37.614 --> 06:39.790
WELL, I DON'T GET A LOT
OF PATIENT COMPLAINTS.

06:39.834 --> 06:40.922
[laughs]

06:40.965 --> 06:42.880
IT'S FUNNY THAT YOU WORK
IN THE MORGUE

06:42.924 --> 06:46.580
BECAUSE MY NAME
IS MORG-AN.

06:46.623 --> 06:50.540
PLEASE WAIT.
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

06:50.584 --> 06:51.585
NOPE.

06:51.628 --> 06:53.674
NOTHING. SORRY.

06:53.717 --> 06:55.240
[sighs]
UH, DR. REED.

06:55.284 --> 06:56.590
DID YOU SEE ME
HIT ON THAT GIRL?

06:56.633 --> 06:57.765
UNFORTUNATELY,
I DID, YES.

06:57.808 --> 06:59.767
I'VE HAD MY EYE ON HER
FOR A WHILE.

06:59.810 --> 07:00.942
I'M GONNA TAKE HER
TO THE BATTING CAGES,

07:00.985 --> 07:02.334
IF YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN.

07:02.378 --> 07:03.727
WELL, LET ME KNOW
HOW THAT DOESN'T WORK OUT.

07:03.771 --> 07:05.076
OKAY, HERE'S MY PLAN.
I AM GOING

07:05.120 --> 07:06.904
TO PUT THESE
IN THE LADIES' ROOM

07:06.948 --> 07:08.645
IN ALL THE STALLS.

07:08.689 --> 07:10.473
"ME WITH OUT GO"--NO, NO, READ IT UP--

07:10.517 --> 07:11.605
OH. "WILL YOU GO OUT
WITH ME?"

07:11.648 --> 07:13.520
AND THEN SHE'LL BE
LIKE, "WHAT?

07:13.563 --> 07:14.956
YES."

07:14.999 --> 07:18.350
MORGAN, WHAT IF SOMEBODY USES
THE BATHROOM BEFORE HER?

07:18.394 --> 07:19.308
YEP, NOT A GOOD IDEA.

07:19.351 --> 07:20.614
PLAN "B."

07:20.657 --> 07:22.485
SURPRISE HER
IN HER CAR TONIGHT.

07:22.529 --> 07:24.269
THAT'S A FELONY.NOT ON VALENTINE'S DAY.

07:24.313 --> 07:25.706
DOESN'T MATTER
WHAT THE HOLIDAY IS.CHECK THE LAWS IN THIS COUNTRY.

07:25.749 --> 07:27.142
I'M NOT EVEN SURE
ABOUT THAT.

07:27.185 --> 07:30.493
[sighs]
MORGAN, WAIT.

07:30.537 --> 07:31.842
MAYBE I COULD HELP YOU.

07:31.886 --> 07:32.843
REALLY?

07:32.887 --> 07:34.758
OH, GOD,
THAT WOULD BE SO GOOD.

07:34.802 --> 07:35.933
[banging at door]

07:35.977 --> 07:38.545
COMING, I'M COMING.

07:38.588 --> 07:39.589
HEY.
HEY.

07:39.633 --> 07:41.025
WHY ARE YOU SO EARLY?

07:41.069 --> 07:42.766
