07:42.810 --> 07:43.767
YOU'RE TEN MINUTES
EARLY, DANNY,

07:43.811 --> 07:45.508
WHICH IS WORSE
THAN TWO HOURS LATE.

07:45.552 --> 07:46.727
THOSE LAST TEN MINUTES,

07:46.770 --> 07:49.469
THAT'S WHEN I GO FROM "WHOA"
TO "DAMN."

07:49.512 --> 07:50.687
WAIT A MINUTE.

07:50.731 --> 07:53.037
WHY DID I HAVE TO COME
HERE FIRST, ANYWAYS?

07:53.081 --> 07:54.691
WELL, YOU ARE GOING
ON A DATE WITH MY FRIEND.

07:54.735 --> 07:56.084
MM-HMM.AND I WANTED TO MAKE SURE

07:56.127 --> 07:57.651
THAT YOU DIDN'T LOOK WEIRD.

07:57.694 --> 07:59.087
YOU HAD, LIKE,
A MUSTACHE OR SOMETHING.

07:59.130 --> 08:01.698
HOW WOULD I GROW A MUSTACHE
SINCE THIS MORNING?

08:01.742 --> 08:02.917
I DON'T KNOW.
I'M NOT ITALIAN.

08:02.960 --> 08:04.266
ALSO, IT'S GOOD
WHEN I'M GETTING PRETTY

08:04.309 --> 08:05.354
FOR THERE TO BE A GUY HERE,
SO HE CAN BE LIKE,

08:05.397 --> 08:06.355
"HURRY UP!
WE'RE GONNA BE LATE!"

08:06.398 --> 08:08.749
WHAT?

08:08.792 --> 08:09.793
